Context / Pain Points
- Initial load produces major delays plus large volumes of warnings and CORS errors.
- Logs are noisy and hard to interpret.
- Need BNS (.btc) name resolution for addresses.
- Need a detailed external integration doc so marketplaces can reconstruct Xtrata inscriptions from chunks.

